import { Box, Center, Flex, Heading, Image, Text } from "@chakra-ui/react";
import React from "react";


const Home = () => {
  return <Box id="home" w='70px' h='10' bg='red.500'>
     <Flex p={10}  >
      <Center><Box>
    <Heading>Hey ! I'm Shivam</Heading>
    <Text>Full stack web Developer</Text>
      </Box>
      <Box w="70%">
      <Image
  borderRadius='full'
  boxSize='150px'
  src='https://bit.ly/dan-abramov'
  alt='Dan Abramov'
/>
      </Box></Center>
     </Flex>
  </Box>
};

export default Home;
